It was delicious.

00:44:50.079 --> 00:44:52.559
You know, the only person that had it was,
where?

00:44:52.559 --> 00:44:54.680
I saw one hand raised.

00:44:54.680 --> 00:44:55.680
And how did you like it?

00:44:55.680 --> 00:44:56.680
&gt;&gt;Male #3: It was good.

00:44:56.680 --> 00:44:57.680
&gt;&gt;Greg Koch: Good.

00:44:57.680 --> 00:45:01.000
&gt;&gt;Male #3: I always try a Saison whenever
I can.

00:45:01.000 --> 00:45:02.990
&gt;&gt;Greg Koch: So, we'll have a chance again.

