It's called now Liberty Station and we're
working to go in and build--opening late this

00:45:23.460 --> 00:45:32.779
fall, I hope--23 thousand square foot under
roof restaurant and brewery with about an

00:45:32.779 --> 00:45:34.880
acre of outdoor space.

