And then, we've got the Stone Packaging Hall,
which will go directly adjacent to our existing

00:45:38.779 --> 00:45:40.809
brewery to allow us to continue to expand.

00:45:40.809 --> 00:45:45.510
We'll kick all the bottling and kegging out
of our current building into this new building.

00:45:45.510 --> 00:45:46.510
Well.

